        "#Now similar to using Q-learning to figure out what the optimal number of generated fake news artciles that should be used in training similar to \n",
        "#LSTM earlier. #This step is immensily lengthy in run time not reccomended. Easier to use LSTM to determine optimal amount and use to imrpove the accuracy of the BERT classifier.\n",
